Scorpios, this month makes 10 years since I first started #ScorpioMystique on Twitter, and it’s been 8 years since i’ve been writing daily scopes. i love this community and my work so deeply, so much that it doesn’t often feel like work, it feels like play! and yet, i must still rest and recalibrate, and this Cancer New Moon is the perfect time for me to make a shift 🦋 (my Mars is in Cancer, and go look at the number of posts on my page… aligned AF ✨)

.
.

.
.
thank you for being here ♏️♥️✨ Love Always, @dossevia 🦂
